AS Kigali vs AS Muhanga

AS Kigali 2-1 AS Muhanga

Uko umukino uri kugenda

Umwanditsi

: Eric Tony Ukurikiyimfura

Amafoto

: Ntare Julius

17:50

AS Kigali iraye ku mwanya wa gatandatu

Gutsinda uyu mukino bifashije AS Kigali gufata umwanya wa gatandatu n'amanota 37 mu gihe AS Muhanga igumye ku mwanya wa cyenda n'amanota 32.

Turabashimiye cyane mwese twabanye uyu munsi, tuzongere kuri uyu wa Gatandatu ku mukino uzahuza Amagaju FC na Rayon Sports i Nyamagabe guhera saa 15:30.

17:46

Mu yindi mikino: Mukura itsindiwe i Kirehe

Undi mukino w'umunsi wa 27 wa shampiyona wahuzaga Kirehe FC na Mukura Victory Sports urangiye ikipe iri mu rugo itsinze ibitego 2-1. Kirehe FC ihise igira amanota 24, ikomeza kugira icyizere cyo kuguma mu cyiciro cya mbere kuko ubu irushwa amanota atatu na Gicumbi FC ya 14 mu gihe hasigaye imikino itatu ngo shampiyona irangire.

17:41

Umukino urarangiye: AS Kigali yegukanye amanota y'umunsi

AS Kigali itsinze umukino w'umunsi wa 27 wa shampiyona yari yakiriyemo AS Muhanga ku bitego 2-1.

17:37

85' AS Muhanga iri gusatira bikomeye

Habimana Youssuf yinjiye mu rubuga rw'amahina ahagana mu ruhande, arekure umuzinga w'ishoti, Bate Shamiru ananirwa kurifata, umupira ushyirwa muri koruneri na ba myugariro ba AS Kigali.

17:35

84' Ikarita y'umuhondo

Ngandu Omar agiye kwishimira mu maso y'umusifuzi ko penaliti atanze itagiye mu izamu, ahita ahabwa ikarita y'umuhondo.

17:34

83' AS Muhanga ihushije penaliti

Nsengiyumva Idrissa acometse umupira imbere usanga Bizimana Yannick ugushijwe mu rubuga rw'amahina na Ngandu Omar. Penaliti itewe na Lulihoshi Aksante Dieu Merci, umupira ujya hejuru y'izamu

17:31

80' Abatoza ba AS Muhanga ntibabyumva

Mu gihe AS Muhanga ikomeje gusatira cyane ishaka igitego cyo kwishyura, Ndayishimiye Dieudonne ateranye umupira Niyomugabo Jean Claude awukora n'ukuboko mu rubuga rw'amahina, Abdu Mbarushimana n'abo bafatanya ntibumva uburyo badahawe penaliti.

17:29

77' Gusimbuza kwa AS Muhanga

Kubwamarayika Silas yinjiye mu kibuga asimbura Bigirimana Shabani

17:27

76' AS Muhanga ihushije ibitego byabazwe

Habimana Youssuf ahinduye umupira mwiza mu rubuga rw'amahina, usanga Nsengiyumva Idrissa ushatse gutera yitonze umupira ugarurwa na ba myugariro ba AS kigali. Bizimana Yannick na we abonye uburyo bwiza umupira ushyirwa muri koruneri.

17:26

74' Gusimbuza kwa AS Muhanga

Munyeshuri Aaron ahise asimburwa na Nsengiyumva Idrissa

17:24

74' Ikarita y'umuhondo

70' Igitego cya kabiri cya AS Kigali

AS Kigali ibonye koruneri ebyiri ku mipira irengejwe na Twagirayezu Fabien. Ishimwe Kevin ateye umupira usanga Nsabimana Eric imbere y'izamu, azamuka mu kirere asimba abandi, atsindira ikipe ye igitego cya kabiri n'umutwe.

17:13

64' Gusimbuza kwa AS Muhanga

17:08

36' Gusimbuza kwa AS Kigali

30' AS Kigali yongeye guhusha igitego

16:20

Mu yindi mikino: I Kirehe naho imvura ni nyinshi

Mukanya gato gashize umukino uri guhuza Kirehe FC na Mukura Victory Sports na wo wahagaritswe n'imvura nyinshi yaguye mu Burasirazuba. Mukura Victory Sports yatsinze igitego ku munota wa 13 gitsinzwe na Ndizeye Innocent.

16:14

20' AS Kigali ihushije igitego cyabazwe

Harerimana Rashid Leo ahinduye umupira mwiza mu rubuga rw'amahina, uturutse ku ruhande rw;iburyo, usanga kapiteni wa AS Kigali, Murengezi Rodrigue mu rubuga rw'amahina, ashyizeho umutwe ujya hejuru gato y'izamu.

16:12

15' Gusatira kwa AS Kigali

Rutahizamu w'Umugande ukinira AS Kigali, Frank Kalanda, agerageje ishoti rikomeye umupira uramutenguha ujya hanze. Amakipe yombi akomeje gukina umupira ugenda hejuru kuko hasi batabasha guhererekanya inshuro zirenze ebyiri

16:05

10' Igitego cya AS Muhanga

AS Muhanga yari imaze akanya ikina neza, ibonye igitego cyo kwishyura gitsinzwe na kapiteni wayo Hakundukize Adolphe wungukiye ku mupira utewe na Rurangwa Mossi ashaka guha umunyezamu Bate Shamiru, umupira ntiwagera kure kubera amaze, ufatwa na Adophe witonze aroba Bate Shamiru.

16:00

6' Igitego cya AS Kigali

Ishimwe Kevin azamukanye umupira mu ruhande rw'ibumoso, yinjira mu rubuga rw'amahina, areba uko abakinnyi b'inyuma ba AS Muhanga bahagaze, abarenza umupira ujya ku rundi ruhande, aho usanze kapiteni we Murengezi Rodrigue ashyiraho umutwe, umunyezamu Munyaneza Jacques yisa nga inshundura zinyeganyega.

15:57

AS kigali igomba kwitonda

AS Muhanga ifite abakinnyi bihuta aho kugeza ubu bamaze kugera ku izamu rya AS Kigali inshuri eshatu. Bizimana Yannick yari ahawe umupira yinjira mu rubuga rw'amahina, umusifuzi avuga ko yabanje gusunika Rurangwa Mossi

15:55

1' AS Muhanga itangiye isatira

15:53

Umukino uratangiye
